transcript:
Executive: Hello?
Customer: Yeah, good morning, Anita.
Executive: Ha, good morning, ma'am. Aaj hua ma'am kuch?
Customer: Ha, aaj ho jayega aapka. Maine production team se baat kar li hai. Woh bas aapka finalize kar rahe hain. Matlab like jo catalogue hai woh wapas se check out karke sara kuch details dekh rahe hain. Uske baad fir aaj ho jayega done.
Customer: Toh ma'am around kitne baje tak?
Executive: Accha time toh abhi maine unse pucha nahi. Ek bar ruk jaiye, main unse connect karke time puch le rahi hu ki kab tak woh complete kar lenge.
Customer: Hmm.
Executive: Theek hai. Ho jayega. Okay.
Customer: Okay.
